{"tid":1114114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[生命教育]學校還原車禍現場 特技演員慘被真撞死","createTime":"2019-04-18T09:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T11:40:15.000Z","uid":1065,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3209ec4616a67be4484f22f1504b8bf474c26a41","tid":1114114,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/982483-國際-弄假成真！學校還原車禍現場+特技演員慘被真撞死\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F982483-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%BC%84%E5%81%87%E6%88%90%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%81%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%2B%E7%89%B9%E6%8A%80%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E6%85%98%E8%A2%AB%E7%9C%9F%E6%92%9E%E6%AD%BB&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=ecedfcc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F982483-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%BC%84%E5%81%87%E6%88%90%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%81%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%2B%E7%89%B9%E6%8A%80%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E6%85%98%E8%A2%AB%E7%9C%9F%E6%92%9E%E6%AD%BB&h=bd7b9e7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/982483-國際-弄假成真！學校還原車禍現場+特技演員慘被真撞死</a><br />\n<br />\n日本京都山科區平田町一間中學上周五（12日）請來特技演員，重現車禍現場，以此教育學生交通安全的重要性。怎料，在演示過程中發生意外，特技演員當場被貨車撞傷，7小時後不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據日本媒體報道，當地勸修中學和交通安全教室共同舉辦的一個活動中，請來了34歲的特技演員中村佳宏。按照計劃，他將扮演路人，誤入貨車司機的視綫死角，被時速10公里的貨車撞上。令人沒想到的是，在演示過程中意外發生了。中村被卡車撞倒後，雙手雖然盡快去抓住了保險槓，但此後在過程中不慎鬆了手，身體下落被卡車推著在地上摩擦前行。他看起來非常痛苦，不斷大叫。一場教學活動就這樣真的成為了一場意外事故，中村胸腹等部位遭受嚴重擠壓，被送醫7小時後不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據報，當時有大約470名學生在現場目睹了整個過程。事實上，為了讓學生們感受到恐怖實感，類似的教學活動從2016年起進行過6次，但此前都不曾真的發生事故。對此，當地政府表示，考慮到學生的心理狀況，今年將終止類似的教育活動。<br />\n<br />\n事故發生後，中村所在的公司發表聲明，對參加教育活動的學生和相關人員表示抱歉，並稱未來會更加注重安全，也會為死去的中村祈福，對其家人致以歉意。<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dc9133dc6e1d2d14a4efeac0aeeba3e14749f9","tid":1114114,"uid":174289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"用生命教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRip"},{"pid":"d4bd2dbb960a0868056cc3ca8c29e4dc6b3204fa","tid":1114114,"uid":125213,"like":4,"dislike":32,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:47:11.000Z","msg":"對唔住 笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86df36827963001e47a47a21b47e6350e0a55ab","tid":1114114,"uid":41660,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"用生命影響生命"},{"pid":"5c5e6a45e884e985e0c94c1bb590518677c37fbf","tid":1114114,"uid":9013,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n雖然無左條生命，但我深信呢個教育一定刻骨銘心<br />\n希望果班小朋友學到野"},{"pid":"9ccada935dbaa169e38254f860cb146658d3222d","tid":1114114,"uid":55531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"係鴻興呀標哥要我黎殺你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3927701e23b9dc058ca9396cecca5cf1c3b834c","tid":1114114,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffb51bf5e0d74f77bdc9050f1cb86ee2889cfc1","tid":1114114,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"可能有人響保險桿搽左野，令佢捉唔實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：睇開金田一"},{"pid":"8c5a30ec4a2771c298e389086d9346f8320f45c0","tid":1114114,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"時速10公里 學生都唔會認真喇吓"},{"pid":"814edd9d60a0cdda56e4ba1d14dccaafb6b30ce2","tid":1114114,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"震撼教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}